title: Beautiful Community Near The Lake! Dog Park, Fitness Classes!
posting_body: ['Charming community that provides a comfortable living lifestyle in a tranquil, suburban setting.', 'Tucked away from the hustle and bustle of Dallas city living, Bella Madera Apartments is still only moments from major business districts, shopping areas, places of worship, recreation, and much more.', 'With its spacious one and two bedroom floor plans, complete with a convenient location and a myriad of luxurious amenities, Bella Madera Apartments achieves the perfect balance of convenience and luxury at an affordable price.', 'Extraordinary Lifestyle', 'Elegant Italian Architectural Styling', 'Resort-Style Swimming Pool', 'Cascading Fountains w/ Conversation Areas', 'Professionally Equipped Cardio Center', 'Free Fitness Classes', 'Clubroom w/ Fireplace and Conversation Area', 'Complimentary Tanning Studio', 'Executive Business Center', 'Two New Dog Parks', 'Lush Landscaping Throughout', 'Please call Desiree', 'show contact info', 'Dash Apartment Locators!', 'Mention Ad D-28']
